The '''Body Calculus''' was a governmental body on [[Yag'Dhul/Legends|Yag'Dhul]]. It was composed of the most revered mathematicians of the [[Givin/Legends|Givin]] people, and based its decisions on mathematical modeling. The Givin government was referred to by outsiders as a [[theocracy]] at the time of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. The Body Calculus published charts and graphs explaining its [[Secession of Yag'Dhul|secession]] from the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]] in [[22 BBY/Legends|22 BBY]].

